      "text": "それとも、もしかしてBIG4になって大人気の\nこころを出待ちでもしてたんですか～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Or maybe‚ were you waiting for Kokoro‚\nwho’s become super popular after becoming BIG4~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.8666666667,
