      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_11_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それは興味深いが今から企画書を作りに……\nうーん、まぁ少しならいいか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s interesting‚ but I have to make a project proposal now…\nHmm‚ well‚ a little is fine.",
        "id": ""
